&lt;p&gt;We are a user-driven company and are committed to making sure every pixel of our product is in service of the clinician. We’re a team of technologists, clinicians, and industry experts working together to push the limits on technology used in medicine. We’re confident enough to move fast and talented enough not to break things. Check out this&lt;a href=&quot;https://resources.suki.ai/vimeo-all-videos/suki-announces-series-c&quot;&gt; short video&lt;/a&gt; to learn more about our mission and our culture.&lt;/p&gt;
